{"tid":1519682,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［831全民運動日］District app - 城市定向遊戲","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:38.000Z","uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8145940dbec9262a4882e489e5acab6914b09696","tid":1519682,"uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"街跑是近年愈來愈受歡迎的運動項目之一，有見及此，澳洲人Ben研發District app，希望大家可以一邊跑步，一邊發掘自己的社區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDistrict 的對象都是大城市，特別之處就是有無窮無盡的探索空間，「以香港為例，我敢說香港的變化多端讓大家可能一輩子都不能完全探索整個香港。」<br />\n<br />\nDistrict app 是一個完全免費的應用程式，香港現家可以到尖沙咀、跑馬地、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">西環</span></span></strong>等社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環地圖版面，設有多個關卡：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFZDTdU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFZDTdU.png&h=22215660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免費下載及玩樂：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOQjCFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOQjCFB.png&h=1fc754d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3562abec1abf1be3ffb7ca9fd7065a1fb9374c96","tid":1519682,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckw